            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Traditional SEO targets rankings in national or global organic search results. Local SEO targets the Local Pack and local organic results for searches with geographic intent. Local SEO uses Google Business Profile, NAP citations, and proximity signals that do not apply to national SEO.</p></div></div>
          </div>
